author: COMSOL
description: This example illustrates the modeling of convective and conductive heat transfer in a unit cell of a MEMS heat exchanger, commonly found in lab-on-chip devices. The example uses the Heat Transfer interface, applying an analytical velocity profile to describe the laminar flow of water through the tubes.
